---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — PDF Tools" description="What pdf.oriz.in is and isn't." hideSidebar={true}>
  <header class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">PDF Tools</a> / <a href="/legal/">Legal</a> / Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="prose">
    <p>
      Everything on pdf.oriz.in is published in good faith for general use only.
      Use it at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Tool outputs are not legally binding</h2>
    <p>
      Tools like Sign PDF, Redact PDF, and Protect PDF perform the requested
      operations but do not by themselves make a document legally binding,
      regulator-grade redacted, or unbreakable. Where legal validity matters
      (e.g. court filings, regulated industries), use a qualified service.
    </p>

    <h2>Not legal advice</h2>
    <p>
      Articles touching on document law, signatures, or compliance reflect the
      author's reading of the rules at the time of writing. Rules change.
      Verify with your own counsel before acting.
    </p>

    <h2>Not medical or financial advice</h2>
    <p>
      Anything you read on the site about health or finance is for general
      awareness only. It is not a substitute for consultation with a registered
      practitioner or SEBI-registered investment advisor.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      We link to third-party sites we find useful. We don't control their
      content, and inclusion is not an endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Where applicable, pdf.oriz.in may earn a referral fee when you sign up to
      a service via certain links. This never affects what we recommend, and
      any such links will be marked.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { max-width: var(--container-prose, 720px); margin-inline: auto; padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-fg-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow a { color: var(--color-fg-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif, Georgia, serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }
  .meta { color: var(--color-fg-soft); font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .prose { max-width: var(--container-prose, 720px); margin-inline: auto; padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem; color: var(--color-prose); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.0625rem; }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif, Georgia, serif); font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
</style>
